@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Budgets";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="about-content">
    <p>
        Welcome to the Budget section! Here, you can manage your personal finances by setting up and organizing budgets.
        Tracking your expenses, income, and bills is essential to staying on top of your financial goals. Our budgeting tool
        is designed to empower you to take control of your financial future with ease and confidence.
    </p>

    <h2>Why Budgeting Matters</h2>
    <p>
        Creating and sticking to a budget is a crucial step toward achieving financial stability and success.
        Budgeting helps you understand your spending habits, identify areas for improvement, and plan for future expenses.
        Whether you want to save for a dream vacation, pay off debt, or simply get a better grip on your finances,
        our budgeting features can help you get there.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Features of Our Budgeting Tool</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Create multiple budgets for different purposes, such as household, travel, or savings. Tailor your budgets to fit your unique lifestyle and goals.</li>
        <li>Monitor your spending and receive summaries of your financial activity. Our intuitive dashboard provides a clear overview of your finances, making it easy to see where your money is going.</li>
        <li>Plan ahead with categorized expense tracking and forecasting features. Gain insights into your spending trends and make informed decisions about future expenses.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Managing Your Budget</h2>
    <p>
        Effectively managing your budget is essential for achieving your financial objectives. Here are some key strategies:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Creating Personalized Budget Categories:</strong> Customize your budget categories based on your lifestyle and priorities. This allows you to allocate funds where they matter most, whether it’s groceries, entertainment, or savings.</li>
        <li><strong>Setting Spending Limits:</strong> Establish clear limits for each category to help control your spending. Setting realistic limits encourages disciplined financial behavior and prevents overspending.</li>
        <li><strong>Monitoring Progress:</strong> Regularly review your budget to track your progress. Our tool provides visual representations of your spending versus your budget, helping you stay accountable and make necessary adjustments.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Get Started Today!</h2>
    <p>
        Begin your budgeting journey today and take control of your financial future. By effectively managing your budgets,
        you’ll gain greater financial awareness, make informed decisions, and achieve your goals faster. Remember, every
        small step you take brings you closer to financial freedom!
    </p>
</div>
